Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用性急到站着吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她在1班对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的情报
