Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是Rock啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那之后 小秋非常投入
