Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该结束了吧
